.SH SEE ALSO
.sp
.LP
\fBauditconfig\fR(1M), \fBauditd\fR(1M), \fBaudit_startup\fR(1M),
\fBaudit.log\fR(4), \fBaudit_control\fR(4), \fBattributes\fR(5)
.sp
.LP
See the section on Solaris Auditing in \fISystem Administration Guide:
Security Services\fR.
.SH NOTES
.sp
.LP
\fBbsmconv\fR and \fBbsmunconv\fR are not valid in a non-global zone.
.sp
.LP
These commands are Obsolete and may be removed and replaced with equivalent
functionality in a future release of Solaris.
